Hello,

Thank you for your time during the remote connection.
To resolve the connection issue, please edit the options.sh as we did in the meeting, then reinstall the Epp client.
You can try to run the install.sh after editing the options.sh to see if the IP changes in the Epp client window after you press ctrl + alt + i on the settings tab.
If that does not work, please reinstall the client as we did in the meeting.

Please let us know your result after testing this on more computers.

Kind regards
